15:38.271 --> 15:39.973
I'm sorry, Bev.

15:40.040 --> 15:41.408
Guess this money is yours.

15:41.474 --> 15:43.843
No, it's for your business.
It's just a bump in the road.

15:43.910 --> 15:45.478
Just keep it.

15:45.545 --> 15:47.981
And all your loving support.

15:49.949 --> 15:52.785
The jackets were a failure
and so am I.

15:59.726 --> 16:03.063
ADULT ADAM: Even though
Barry was making the Eagles
crush the Patriots,

16:03.130 --> 16:05.365
his real life football career
was done.

16:05.432 --> 16:06.766
Hey, don't you have
a game tonight?

16:06.833 --> 16:09.169
